comments: Shamet (BKN) maintain legal guarding position as he absorbs the contact  initiated by Ariza (MIA) while contesting his driving shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Brown (BKN) firms up and absorbs the contact.
Iguodala (MIA) makes marginal contact to the arm of Irving (BKN) during the drive that does not affect his SQBR.
Iguodala (MIA) makes incidental high five contact to the off hand of Irving (BKN) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Brown (BKN) makes marginal contact to the body of Dragic (MIA) during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) makes contact to the arm of Green (BKN) during his drive that causes him to lose possession of the ball momentarily.

While receiving the inbound pass Green (BKN) fails to completely gain control of the ball and he bobbles it before bringing both hands to the ball and regaining full control.  He does not move his pivot foot after regaining possession of the ball.
Adebayo (MIA) makes incidental high five contact to the hand of Irving (BKN) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Harris (BKN) is moving in a straight-line path in transition and Dragic (MIA) veers into him to create the marginal contact.
During the drive with 1.8 seconds remaining, Adebayo (MIA) places his off-arm against Green (BKN) and releases from contact without extending into him.
